The loop currently isn't executed for the last value of the range. I'd do something like




        Suggested change











            		if (fromValue == toValue) {



            			return true;



            		}







            		if (getCurrentIteration() == toValue) {



            			return true;



            		}







            		return false;



            		return executedCount == Math.abs(toValue - fromValue) + 1;






and check for invalid types (float, String, ...) at the beginning.

